Catalyst::Plugin::ForwardChained

Forwarding to "Chain"-Actions in Catalyst

01. INSTALLATION

To install this module perform the typical four-part Perl salute:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

02. MODULE REQUIREMENTS

    Archive::Tar >= 1.40
    Cache::FastMmap
    Cache::File
    Cache::Memcached
    Crypt::OpenSSL::RSA
    DateTime
    DBD::SQLite
    DBI
    DBIx::Connector
    Email::Valid
    Getopt::Long
    IO::File
    IO::Handle
    IO::Pipe
    IO::Socket
    IO::YAML >= 0.08
    IPC::Semaphore >= 2.01
    IPC::SysV >= 2.01
    Mail::DKIM >= 0.38
    Mail::SPF
    MIME::Base64
    MIME::Lite
    MIME::Parser
    MIME::QuotedPrint
    Moose >= 1.00
    Net::Domain::TLD
    Net::DNS
    Net::DNSBL::Client
    Net::LMTP
    Net::Milter
    Net::Netmask
    Net::SMTP
    POE
    POE::Filter::Postfix::Plain
    POE::Wheel::FollowTail
    POE::Wheel::ReadWrite
    POE::Wheel::SocketFactory
    Regexp::Common
    SQL::Abstract
    Throwable
    version >= 0.74
    YAML

To use the Policy GeoWeight module, you have to install Geo::IP, which relys on OS libraries.

